Sentencas: Nanocrystalline triple-doped ceria based solid electrolyte materials (CuxMn0.1-x Zr0.1Ce0.8O2, where x = 0, 0.02, 0.04, 0.06, 0.08 and 0.1, as well as Cu0.08Mn0.02ZryCe0.9-yO2, where y = 0 and 0.1) for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells were successfully synthesized by co-precipitation method with sonication and sintered at 1150 degrees C for 4 h in air.
Titulo: Electrical properties of Cu-Mn-Zrco-doped ceria electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell application
